  * Statistics that previously resided in another draft have been moved here to keep the data context-appropriate.
  * While the draft is stable, it cannot progress to Working Group Last Call (WGLC) until [draft-ietf-grow-bmp-tlv](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-grow-bmp-tlv) (BMP v4) is finalized.

