* **Adj-RIB-In and Adj-RIB-Out Filtering (`draft-ietf-grow-bmp-adj-ribs-filtered`)**:
  * Proposes adding a "filtered flag" to Adj-RIB-In and Adj-RIB-Out messages, mirroring the existing Loc-RIB capability.
