## Decisions and Action Items

* **ADJ-RIB-In/Out Filtering**: The chairs will issue a Working Group Last Call for [draft-ietf-grow-bmp-adj-ribs-filtered](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-grow-bmp-adj-ribs-filtered).
* **BMP v4 Scope**: The working group agreed to keep [draft-ietf-grow-bmp-tlv](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-grow-bmp-tlv) stable and wrap it up for publication. Major modifications (such as transitioning static peer headers into TLVs) will be deferred to a future "BMP v5" design team.
* **BMP Scaling & Event Merges**: The authors of the individual BMP scaling and notification drafts will proceed with merging the common updates draft into the aggregated route monitoring draft, and coordinate on a single event reporting framework with [draft-ietf-grow-bmp-rel](https://datatracker.ietf.org/id/draft-ietf-grow-bmp-rel).

